Rating: 4
This was a very good and easy entree for a party. They got rave reviews and were simple to make. To make 4 dinner-plate sized trays for a cocktail party, I used the following ingredients: 4 cups blue cheese crumbles 2 cups spicy nuts (I used walnuts) 12 Tbsp honey 12 endives The filling is rich, so a little (about 1 Tbsp) goes a long way in the endive leaf.

